Davina McCall, 54, regularly shows off her gym-honed physique and today was no different. The presenter shared a video to Instagram from her recent sunny Turkey getaway as she danced for the camera. She turned heads as she danced around in a tiny yellow bikini, showing off her abs and toned body. The former Big Brother host even twerked for the camera, oozing confidence and enjoying her sun-soaked getaway. Davina captioned the video in view of her 1.5 million followers: "Fun day at twerk."